    • Method Detail

      • resolveType

        <T> Class<? extends T> resolveType​(Class<T> declaredType,
                                   org.springframework.hateoas.Links resourceLinks,
                                   Configuration configuration)
        Get the type to use for a resource. This will be the superclass of proxies generated for the properties (or property collection items) returning the resource, and so must be a subtype of the property's (or property collection item's) declared type.
        Parameters:
        declaredType - declared type of the property or property collection item
        resourceLinks - links of the resource
        configuration - client factory configuration
        Returns:
        the type to use for the superclass of the generated proxy for a resource
